{"tid":1106946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爬簷篷扑爛大玻璃 賊潛咖啡室爆竊","createTime":"2019-04-15T01:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T01:49:43.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2994f6fbf098fbc0ca9ffdb0a7f222a0520a0f61","tid":1106946,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T01:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1qf5Zv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1qf5Zv.png&h=c87c4789&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1f5vUSR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1f5vUSR.png&h=29100127&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YWvarb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YWvarb.png&h=d9e286b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咖啡室收銀機及夾萬被人撬開。潘志能攝<br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪邨商場一間越南咖啡室，凌晨5時許，姓徐44歲女職員返回，發現店舖外牆玻璃碎裂，店舖遭爆竊，收銀機及夾萬撬開，於是報警。警員到場調查，初步相信賊人爬上1樓簷篷，用硬物擊碎該塊4呎乘5呎的大玻璃，竄入店內搜掠，經負責人點算損失約7萬元。警方列爆竊案處理，交由秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊跟進。"}]}